{"tid":974454,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[無圖]芬蘭十日無極光鳩hea遊記","createTime":"2019-01-09T01:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T15:43:54.000Z","uid":68478,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"07d9824028832e4bca7e71d90b2ae526a9adfa88","tid":974454,"uid":68478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T01:33:25.000Z","msg":"*呢篇係自己打番比自己睇*<br />\n<br />\n幾年前開始，就有個想冬天去芬蘭睇極光既諗頭<br />\n如果今次唔係同行個fd比我有植入咗個念頭<br />\n想三十歲前睇到，成個Trip都唔會發生<br />\n係十月份終於買咗香港來回Helsinki 機票<br />\n亦開始慢慢book 其他嘢<br />\n因為我哋都有拖延癌<br />\n如果唔落實嘅嘢我哋真係會一拖再拖<br />\n而玻璃屋亦係我地既wish list 入面<br />\n玻璃屋一向都難book<br />\n我哋嘅出發日期係一月頭<br />\n當時check過d酒店中介網<br />\n好似得返木屋前面有玻璃頂個隻<br />\n8000幾一晚，而唔係我哋一直想住半圓頂<br />\n直到11月幾，我上佢官網搵搵下<br />\n發現small igloos 重available <br />\n就即刻訂左係個fd生日時住<br />\n兩晚盛惠11000幾<br />\n我(地)都一直懶懶閒無plan d咩<br />\n只係略略分左大概去既城市而book既住宿同內陸機票<br />\n我本身直頭想只book第一晚<br />\n之後又到時先算，但我fd比較怕死<br />\n所以最後係<br />\nDay1-3 Rovaniemi <br />\nDay4-6 Ivalo<br />\nDay7-10 Helsinki"},{"pid":"a317fe74fd3d8ca6d08c6070da8661327f5bfdee","tid":974454,"uid":68478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T01:53:41.000Z","msg":"聖誕前後做嘢忙到仆街<br />\n都無乜時間準備旅行既野<br />\n終於去到出發嘅日子<br />\n我哋坐凌晨機去<br />\n<br />\nDay1 HKG-Helsinki-Rovaniemi <br />\n1am飛11個鐘到Helsinki 再轉機1個幾鐘到Rovaniemi <br />\n一落機嚇親我，唔係因為凍<br />\n係個機場細到嘔<br />\n條行李帶行兩步已經到門口<br />\n門口又對住個登機位，啲人等上飛機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kam5whR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKam5whR.png&h=fe2ab05f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾有聖誕氣氛<br />\n<br />\n之後我哋搭airport express 去酒店<br />\n佢係的士形式嘅小巴？<br />\n直接送到去酒店門口<br />\n7&euro;一個人<br />\n10零20分鐘就到酒店<br />\n我哋住喺City Centre<br />\n係一間有得煮嘢食嘅apartment <br />\n我地11點去到，無得提早check in <br />\n所以着好衫就寄存左行李<br />\n出去食野同行下<br />\n我地第一餐<br />\n登<br />\n！<br />\n登<br />\n！<br />\n登<br />\n！<br />\n鄧<br />\n！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麥當勞</span></strong>"},{"pid":"fc23ab8a6f95174471c2f31699da93cfeec7dfe6","tid":974454,"uid":68478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T02:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S2ooh2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS2ooh2f.png&h=59f59e8f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XLGQHtX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXLGQHtX.png&h=406c2058&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9i6M0fC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9i6M0fC.png&h=a295af90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47a2yAE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47a2yAE.png&h=816a3b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MvFh6VG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMvFh6VG.png&h=b6c5fc2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由酒店行10分鐘就到全世界第二北麥當勞(最北係俄羅斯)<br />\n想試下有咩分別<br />\n就樣樣叫d，咁就20&euro;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過個麥樂雞好好食，而且有好多味既醬揀<br />\n必食！<br />\n其他無乜特別，新地無花生<br />\n個包特別大，食唔哂<br />\n食完就去左附近超市買水同野食<br />\n由於check過當晚天清，但之後幾日有雲<br />\n我地就決定第一日就join 極光團<br />\n我地係Nordic unique 到book左個攝影團<br />\n點解會揀呢間因爲破冰船都join 左呢度<br />\n查詢完我本身想睇多幾間先<br />\n因為我想要細團，係Hunting light 果d<br />\n但我fd心急又阿支阿左話重揾黎做乜<br />\n迫於無奈廢事煩就join左，110&euro;一個人3-4個鐘<br />\n包接送，有衫借"},{"pid":"9b86f8baac575e6089e8031b10ad2c0a912fba81","tid":974454,"uid":68478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T02:20:35.000Z","msg":"眼瞓 瞓先<br />\n4:20am <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iCzuX9K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiCzuX9K.png&h=1741c860&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"546518b6391dd9fe284b641e5f38322fafe1d9b9","tid":974454,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T02:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005a29166908afdf0430739938d73